metadata.description:
The title does not translate well because it reads in Japanese with multiple meanings. Sorry.

The Seen World

At least I, the individual that I am, painted it with 10 meanings

What do you see in this picture?

Everything changes depending on how you look at it

How do you see it?



見えるセカイ

私という個は少なくとも10の意味を込めて描きました

あなたはこの絵に何を視ますか

あらゆるものは見方によって変わるもの

あなたはどんな見方をしますか
